videos.description: Stephen A. Smith credits Klay Thompson and Steph Curry for their efforts in Game 2, but details why Andre Iguodala and Draymond Green stood out to him.

videos.description: Mike D'Antoni says under the circumstances of James Harden's injury he thought he played "great."

videos.headline: D'Antoni 'didn't have a doubt' Harden would play with bad eyes

videos.description: Kevin Durant explains how crucial it is for the Warriors to stay focused against the Rockets despite being up 2-0 in the series.

videos.description: James Harden tells reporters after the Rockets' Game 2 loss that he's still in pain after suffering an eye injury and says that everything is 'pretty blurry.'

videos.description: James Harden and Chris Paul say they were "chillin'" on and off the court and deny that there was any chatter about the officiating.
